# Phase 55 CONTRIB-04: path-scoped CODEOWNERS for horus-os.
#
# NO blanket `* @Ridou` assignment. Reviewers are auto-assigned per directory
# so the maintainer sees ownership context for sensitive paths (workflows,
# release scripts, security policy, planning artifacts) while routine
# changes do not block on a default-owner ping.

# CI workflows: every workflow change touches the release pipeline trust chain
/.github/workflows/         @Ridou

# Release-gate and verifier scripts: load-bearing for v0.6 trust substrate
/scripts/release_gate.py    @Ridou
/scripts/verify_release.py  @Ridou

# Security policy: vulnerability disclosure flow
/SECURITY.md                @Ridou

# Planning artifacts: phase decisions, roadmap, requirements
/.planning/                 @Ridou
